      <title>哈萨克斯坦民众称欧洲央行不应“自动”降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/ecb-s-kazaks-says-there-should-be-no-autopilot-after-june-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，欧洲央行在下周预计将采取首次降息举措之后，不应转向“自动驾驶”降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/ecb-s-kazaks-says-there-should-be-no-autopilot-after-june-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
